Source: foundry-emulators-computers
Section: metapackages
Priority: optional
Maintainer: Foundry Linux <packages@foundrylinux.org>
Build-Depends: debhelper-compat (= 13)
Standards-Version: 4.7.0
Homepage: https://foundrylinux.org/
Rules-Requires-Root: no

Package: foundry-emulators-computers
Architecture: all
Depends: ${misc:Depends},
 dosbox-x,
 hatari,
 fs-uae,
 openmsx,
 openmsx-data
Description: vintage home-computer emulators (no bundled ROMs)
 Universe-only emulators that do not ship non-redistributable ROMs in
 the .deb. Suitable for inclusion in container images and ISOs without
 redistribution concerns:
 .
   * dosbox-x        DOS / x86 PC emulator (16-bit + early 32-bit)
   * hatari          Atari ST / STE / TT / Falcon
   * fs-uae          Amiga
   * openmsx         MSX / MSX2 / MSX2+ / turboR
   * openmsx-data    OpenMSX system data files
 .
 Vintage emulators that ship non-redistributable ROMs in the .deb (VICE,
 Atari800, FBZX) live in foundry-emulators-vintage instead.
